# =========================================
# VEDA Official Example 14
# Title: BMI Calculator
# Concepts: ask, calculate, say
# Difficulty: Intermediate
# =========================================

ask weight: Enter your weight (kg):
ask height: Enter your height (meters):

calculate heightSquare: height * height
calculate bmi: weight / heightSquare

say:
say: ===== RESULT =====
say: Your BMI:
say: {bmi}